Package: census.gov
Title: US Census Bureau API Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the US Census Bureau API. Covers ACS
    (1-year and 5-year detailed, subject, profile, comparison tables), decennial
    census (PL, DHC, DP, SF1, SF2), population estimates (PEP), economic census,
    PUMS microdata, and migration flows. Includes variable discovery, search,
    geography helpers, and LLM context injection.
